<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>ID Verification Notification</title>
  <style>
    .head-con {
      width: 100%;
      height: 40px;
      background-color: green;
      color: white;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    h2 {
      color: white;
    }

    section {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      margin: 20px;
    }

    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="head-con">
      <h2 class="head">Thriftify</h2>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section>
    <h2>Congratulations {{name}},</h2>
    <p>
      This is to notify you that your ID verification has been successful. You can now buy, shop, and enjoy our website.
    </p>
    <p>
      You can log into your account by clicking <a href="{{link}}">here</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Kind regards,<br />
      The Thriftify Team
    </p>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
